<a target=_blank href=/theravada.ru/Teaching/Canon/Suttanta/Texts/an10_22-adhivutti-sutta-sv.htm>Rus</a> 
 
  <a target=_blank href=/legacy.suttacentral.net/sc/th/an10.22.html>ไทย</a> 
<a target="_blank" href=/sc/?q=an10.22&lang=pli-eng>SC</a> 
</td>
<td><p>
<span class="pli-lang inputscript-ISOPali" lang="pi">Puna caparaṁ, ānanda, tathāgato anekavihitaṁ pubbenivāsaṁ anussarati, seyyathidaṁ<b>—</b>ekampi jātiṁ dvepi jātiyo …pe… iti sākāraṁ sauddesaṁ anekavihitaṁ pubbenivāsaṁ anussarati. </span><br class="btwntrn">
<span class="eng-lang text-muted font-weight-light" lang="en">Furthermore, the Realized One recollects many kinds of past lives, with features and details. </span>
<br class="styled">
