<td><p>
<span class="pli-lang inputscript-ISOPali" lang="pi">Puna caparaṁ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu yāni tāni sabrahmacārīnaṁ uccāvacāni kiṅkaraṇīyāni<b>—</b>tattha dakkho hoti analaso, tatrūpāyāya vīmaṁsāya samannāgato alaṁ kātuṁ alaṁ saṁvidhātuṁ. </span><br class="btwntrn">
<span class="eng-lang text-muted font-weight-light" lang="en">Furthermore, a mendicant is deft and tireless in a diverse spectrum of duties for their spiritual companions, understanding how to go about things in order to complete and organize the work. … </span>
<br class="styled">
<span class="pli-lang inputscript-ISOPali" lang="pi">Yampi, bhikkhave, bhikkhu yāni tāni sabrahmacārīnaṁ uccāvacāni kiṅkaraṇīyāni<b>—</b>tattha dakkho hoti analaso tatrūpāyāya vīmaṁsāya samannāgato alaṁ kātuṁ alaṁ saṁvidhātuṁ, </span><br class="btwntrn">
