<td><a class="freebutton" target="_blank" href=/sc/?q=an10.93&lang=pli>an10.93</a></td>
<td><strong class="pli-lang inputscript-ISOPali">Kiṁdiṭṭhikasutta </strong>What Is Your View? </td>
