<td><a class="freebutton" target="_blank" href=/sc/?q=an10.121&lang=pli>an10.121</a></td>
<td><strong class="pli-lang inputscript-ISOPali">Pubbaṅgamasutta </strong>Forerunner </td>
<td><div class="wordwrap"></div></td>
<td>2</td>   
<td>0</td>
<td>
<a target=_blank href=/theravada.ru/Teaching/Canon/Suttanta/Texts/an10_121-pubbangama-sutta-sv.htm>Rus</a> 
 
  <a target=_blank href=/legacy.suttacentral.net/sc/th/an10.121.html>ไทย</a> 
<a target="_blank" href=/sc/?q=an10.121&lang=pli-eng>SC</a> 
</td>
<td><p>
<span class="pli-lang inputscript-ISOPali" lang="pi">“Sūriyassa, bhikkhave, udayato etaṁ pubbaṅgamaṁ etaṁ pubbanimittaṁ, yadidaṁ<b>—</b>aruṇuggaṁ. </span><br class="btwntrn">
<span class="eng-lang text-muted font-weight-light" lang="en">“Mendicants, the dawn is the forerunner and precursor of the sunrise. </span>
<br class="styled">
<span class="pli-lang inputscript-ISOPali" lang="pi">Evamevaṁ kho, bhikkhave, kusalānaṁ dhammānaṁ etaṁ pubbaṅgamaṁ etaṁ pubbanimittaṁ, yadidaṁ<b>—</b>sammādiṭṭhi. </span><br class="btwntrn">
<span class="eng-lang text-muted font-weight-light" lang="en">In the same way right view is the forerunner and precursor of skillful qualities. </span>
<br class="styled">
</p></td>
<!-- <td><a target="_blank" href="https://voice.suttacentral.net/scv/index.html?#/sutta?search=an10.121">mp3</a></td> -->
