<td><a class="freebutton" target="_blank" href=/sc/?q=mn14&lang=pli>mn14</a></td>
<td><strong class="pli-lang inputscript-ISOPali">Cūḷadukkhakkhandhasutta </strong>The Shorter Discourse on the Mass of Suffering </td>
<td><div class="wordwrap"></div></td>
<td>3</td>   
<td>0</td>
<td>
<a target=_blank href=/theravada.ru/Teaching/Canon/Suttanta/Texts/mn14-cula-dukkha-kkhandha-sutta-sv.htm>Rus</a> 
 
  <a target=_blank href=/legacy.suttacentral.net/sc/th/mn14.html>ไทย</a> 
<a target="_blank" href=/sc/?q=mn14&lang=pli-eng>SC</a> 
</td>
<td><p>
<span class="pli-lang inputscript-ISOPali" lang="pi">Yato ca kho, mahānāma, ariyasāvakassa ‘appassādā kāmā bahudukkhā bahupāyāsā, ādīnavo ettha bhiyyo’ti<b>—</b>evametaṁ yathābhūtaṁ sammappaññāya sudiṭṭhaṁ hoti, so ca aññatreva kāmehi aññatra akusalehi dhammehi pītisukhaṁ adhigacchati aññaṁ vā tato santataraṁ; </span><br class="btwntrn">
<span class="eng-lang text-muted font-weight-light" lang="en">But when they do achieve that rapture and bliss, or something more peaceful than that, </span>
<br class="styled">
<span class="pli-lang inputscript-ISOPali" lang="pi">‘appassādā kāmā bahudukkhā bahupāyāsā, ādīnavo ettha bhiyyo’ti<b>—</b>evametaṁ yathābhūtaṁ sammappaññāya sudiṭṭhaṁ hoti, </span><br class="btwntrn">
<span class="eng-lang text-muted font-weight-light" lang="en">‘Sensual pleasures give little gratification and much suffering and distress, and they are all the more full of drawbacks.’ </span>
<br class="styled">
<span class="pli-lang inputscript-ISOPali" lang="pi">Yato ca kho me, mahānāma, ‘appassādā kāmā bahudukkhā bahupāyāsā, ādīnavo ettha bhiyyo’ti<b>—</b>evametaṁ yathābhūtaṁ sammappaññāya sudiṭṭhaṁ ahosi, so ca aññatreva kāmehi aññatra akusalehi dhammehi pītisukhaṁ ajjhagamaṁ, aññaṁ vā tato santataraṁ; </span><br class="btwntrn">
<span class="eng-lang text-muted font-weight-light" lang="en">But when I did achieve that rapture and bliss, or something more peaceful than that, </span>
<br class="styled">
</p></td>
<!-- <td><a target="_blank" href="https://voice.suttacentral.net/scv/index.html?#/sutta?search=mn14">mp3</a></td> -->
</tr>
