<td><a class="freebutton" target="_blank" href=/sc/?q=sn1.37&lang=pli>sn1.37</a></td>
<td><strong class="pli-lang inputscript-ISOPali">Samayasutta Devatāsaṁyuttaṁ </strong>The Congregation </td>
<td><div class="wordwrap"></div></td>
<td>2</td>   
<td>1</td>
<td>
<a target=_blank href=/theravada.ru/Teaching/Canon/Suttanta/Texts/sn1_37-samaya-sutta-sv.htm>Rus</a> 
 
  <a target=_blank href=/legacy.suttacentral.net/sc/th/sn1.37.html>ไทย</a> 
