</td>
<td><p>
<span class="pli-lang inputscript-ISOPali" lang="pi">Atha kho tā devatā<b>—</b>seyyathāpi nāma balavā puriso samiñjitaṁ vā bāhaṁ pasāreyya pasāritaṁ vā bāhaṁ samiñjeyya; evameva<b>—</b>suddhāvāsesu devesu antarahitā bhagavato purato pāturahesuṁ. </span><br class="btwntrn">
<span class="eng-lang text-muted font-weight-light" lang="en">Then, as easily as a strong person would extend or contract their arm, they vanished from the Pure Abodes and reappeared in front of the Buddha. </span>
<br class="styled">
</p></td>
