<a target="_blank" href=/sc/?q=sn6.1&lang=pli-eng>SC</a> 
</td>
<td><p>
<span class="pli-lang inputscript-ISOPali" lang="pi">Atha kho brahmā sahampati<b>—</b>seyyathāpi nāma balavā puriso samiñjitaṁ vā bāhaṁ pasāreyya, pasāritaṁ vā bāhaṁ samiñjeyya; evameva<b>—</b>brahmaloke antarahito bhagavato purato pāturahosi. </span><br class="btwntrn">
<span class="eng-lang text-muted font-weight-light" lang="en">Then, as easily as a strong person would extend or contract their arm, he vanished from the Brahmā realm and reappeared in front of the Buddha. </span>
