<td><a class="freebutton" target="_blank" href=/sc/?q=sn6.6&lang=pli>sn6.6</a></td>
<td><strong class="pli-lang inputscript-ISOPali">Brahmalokasutta Brahmasaṁyuttaṁ </strong>The Negligent Brahmā </td>
<td><div class="wordwrap"></div></td>
<td>2</td>   
<td>1</td>
<td>
<a target=_blank href=/theravada.ru/Teaching/Canon/Suttanta/Texts/sn6_6-pamada-sutta-sv.htm>Rus</a> 
 
