<span class="pli-lang inputscript-ISOPali" lang="pi">Atha kho subrahmā ca paccekabrahmā suddhāvāso ca paccekabrahmā<b>—</b>seyyathāpi nāma balavā puriso …pe… evameva<b>—</b>bhagavato purato antarahitā tasmiṁ brahmaloke pāturahesuṁ. </span><br class="btwntrn">
<span class="eng-lang text-muted font-weight-light" lang="en">Then, as easily as a strong person would extend or contract their arm, they vanished from in front of the Buddha and appeared in that Brahmā realm. </span>
