</td>
<td><p>
<span class="pli-lang inputscript-ISOPali" lang="pi">‘Anupavajjaṁ channo bhikkhu satthaṁ āharissatī’ti<b>—</b>evametaṁ, āvuso sāriputta, dhārehī”ti. </span><br class="btwntrn">
<span class="eng-lang text-muted font-weight-light" lang="en">You should remember this: ‘The mendicant Channa will slit his wrists blamelessly.’” </span>
