<td><p>
<span class="pli-lang inputscript-ISOPali" lang="pi">katamaṁ nu kho paṇītataraṁ<b>—</b>ñāṇaṁ vā saddhā vā”ti? </span><br class="btwntrn">
<span class="eng-lang text-muted font-weight-light" lang="en">Which is better<b>—</b>knowledge or faith?” </span>
<br class="styled">
