<td><strong class="pli-lang inputscript-ISOPali">Yonisomanasikārasampadāsutta Maggasaṁyuttaṁ </strong>Accomplishment in Proper Attention (1st) </td>
<td><div class="wordwrap"></div></td>
<td>3</td>   
<td>0</td>
<td>
 
