<td><p>
<span class="pli-lang inputscript-ISOPali" lang="pi">Yadidaṁ<b>—</b>sīlasampadā …pe… </span><br class="btwntrn">
<span class="eng-lang text-muted font-weight-light" lang="en">It’s accomplishment in ethics. …” </span>
<br class="styled">
<span class="pli-lang inputscript-ISOPali" lang="pi">yadidaṁ<b>—</b>chandasampadā …pe… </span><br class="btwntrn">
